'''[[卡莉·費奧麗娜|卡莉·費奧麗娜]]'''於2015年5月4日宣佈投入'''2016年美國總統的競選活動'''，與此同時她正式公佈了她作為候選人的資格的視訊。費奧麗娜是一位前商務主管，曾在2010年被[[共和黨_(美國)|美國共和黨]]提名為[[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[參議員|參議員]]的候選人。<ref name="Wall Street Journal">{{cite news|last1=Epstein|first1=Reid|title=Carly Fiorina to Launch Presidential Campaign on May 4|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/carly-fiorina-to-launch-presidential-campaign-on-may-4-1429732381|accessdate=2015-04-26|publisher=Wall Street Journal|date=2015-04-22|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081405/http://www.wsj.com/articles/carly-fiorina-to-launch-presidential-campaign-on-may-4-1429732381|dead-url=no}}</ref>

菲奥莉娜暂停她的竞选共和党总统候选人提名，在 2016 年 2 月 10 日。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2016/02/10/carly-fiorina-republican-presidential-race/80031768/|title=Carly Fiorina suspends GOP presidential bid|newspaper=USA TODAY|accessdate=2017-07-02|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916233624/https://www.usatoday.com/story/news/politics/elections/2016/02/10/carly-fiorina-republican-presidential-race/80031768/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在 2016 年 4 月 27 日，泰德克鲁兹宣布菲奥莉娜将他的竞选搭档他应该赢得提名。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.aol.com/article/2016/04/27/ted-cruz-to-make-a-major-announcement-in-indiana-at-4-p-m/21351891/|title=Ted Cruz names Carly Fiorina as vice president pick|last=Staff|first=AOL|newspaper=AOL.com|accessdate=2017-07-02|language=en|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927155547/https://www.aol.com/article/2016/04/27/ted-cruz-to-make-a-major-announcement-in-indiana-at-4-p-m/21351891/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她加入前印第安纳州小学一直被他丢了、 他竞选天。克鲁兹暂停他的竞选那天晚上，有效地结束菲奥莉娜的副总统竞选。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/its-donald-trumps-gop-after-ted-cruz-drops-out|title=It’s Donald Trump’s GOP after Ted Cruz drops out|newspaper=MSNBC|accessdate=2017-07-02|archive-date=2017-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170927113258/http://www.msnbc.com/msnbc/its-donald-trumps-gop-after-ted-cruz-drops-out|dead-url=no}}</ref> 选举之后，然而，菲奥莉娜收到一个副总统选举人票失信选举人来自德克萨斯州;其他 37，如承诺，赞成迈克便士。

